'''貝克爾斯'''（Beccles）是英國英格蘭薩福克郡的一個集鎮和[[民政教區|民政教區]]<ref name="OL40">OS Explorer Map OL40: The Broads: (1:25 000) : ISBN 0 319 24086 X.</ref>，位於[[查令十字|查令十字]]東北{{convert|98|mi|km|0}}，[[諾維奇|諾維奇]]東南{{convert|16|mi|km|0}}，伊普斯維奇東北{{convert|33|mi|km|0}}。2011年人口普查時，貝克爾斯有人口10,123人<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11120524&c=beccles&d=16&e=62&g=6467316&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=1&s=1382490001448&enc=1 |title=Check Browser Settings |publisher=Neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk |date= |accessdate=30 April 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150609010132/http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11120524&c=beccles&d=16&e=62&g=6467316&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=1&s=1382490001448&enc=1 |archive-date=2015-06-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

